title: Gazebo sundeck, Carpeting, Monthly Resident Events
posting_body: ['At Foxborough Apartments, we have taken every measure to ensure that your home will be impeccable.', 'From custom designed interiors that have been updated, to the natural beauty of the well maintained grounds and exteriors; we strive to provide the perfect setting for wonderful times and fond memories.', 'Relax at one of our pools that are lined with beautiful gazebos, get fit in our fitness center, access the internet in our new business center, and check out a movie from our recent releases selection.', 'Our professional staff is here for you, to provide prompt, courteous attention to your needs and a comfortable style of living.', '-Monthly Resident Events', '-Patio/Balcony', '-Sunrooms & Drybars', '-Reserved, Covered Parking', '-2012, 2013, 2014, 2015, 2017, 2019  Apartment Ratings - Top Rated Award Recipient', '-Gazebo sundeck', '-Clubhouse', '-Wood Look Flooring', '-Ceiling Fan', '-Bark Park', '-Minutes from DFW Airport', '-Large Closets', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
